Summer Exhibition at the Victoria Hall, Shaldon, Devon, UK 16 to 27 August 2018 (The Visit, Hot Air and Green Flowers 2

The Cause, at the Pavilions,Teignmouth, Devon, UK 24 - 28 Sept 2018. Avenda is creating a new piece of work supporting a tour of the new play by Dreadnaught South West about the suffrage campaign by Emmiline Pankhurst and Millicent Fawcett (The Corsets are Off and they are Not going Back On).
